{"tid":1927732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"譚德塞表揚高普，朗拿甸奴獄中參加5人足球賽","createTime":"2020-03-16T03:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T06:26:48.000Z","uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5c994bb914728bca2dc8e25b4cedd07d953e61ce","tid":1927732,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"世衛總幹事譚德塞表揚英超球隊利物浦領隊高普，指對方之前向球迷發表的公開信，是強大的信息，在疫情下關心及同情社會弱勢階層，這個亦是世衛提倡的觀點。<br />\n<br />\n另外，因使用假護照入境，目前被扣押在巴拉圭一所監獄的巴西退役球星「細哨」朗拿甸奴，在獄中參加一場5人足球賽，他帶領球隊以11:2擊敗對手，個人攻入5球，交出6次助攻，之後各參賽者影大合照。<br />\n<br />\n有網民說即使身在獄中，都剝奪不到足球為朗拿甸奴帶來的快樂。有球迷就說希望自己入獄，到時就有機會與「細哨」一較高下。<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514530-20200315.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514530-20200315.htm&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=df5d088a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514530-20200315.htm&h=ad5a3f8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514530-20200315.htm</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"e9dc44eae269dc4575bed6958b437f65cfce7b3c","tid":1927732,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"回解無端端插段細哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2b7267beb88470346281c00f1bac10e1b25834","tid":1927732,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9dc44eae269dc4575bed6958b437f65cfce7b3c","tid":1927732,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"回解無端端插段細哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:21:57.000Z","msg":"問港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd986f18921dd704aa4033ef7521ecabe39215be","tid":1927732,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"